OL,5, A man with autism is taking supermarket
OL,6, giant Sainsbury's to court for refusing
OL,7, entry to his assistance cat.           
OL,9,FDesigner and writer Ian Fenn says the  
OL,10,Fban on Chloe, who helps him in daily   
OL,11,Flife, is limiting his independence.    
OL,13,FHe says she helps him stay calm, but   
OL,14,Fthe supermarket argues that cats,      
OL,15,Funlike assistance dogs, present risks  
OL,16,Fto food hygiene.                       
OL,18,FThe case is so unusual that it might   
OL,19,Fset a major legal precedent if the law 
OL,20,Fneeds to be examined by top judges.    
